==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Farriery
<hw>Far"ri*er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
art of shoeing horses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The art of preventing, curing, or mitigating
diseases of horses and cattle; the veterinary art.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The place where a smith shoes horses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>far-right</ent>⟦br⟧
